{"tid":945442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"射門多不等於應該入波 - 論 Expected Goal 的用法","createTime":"2018-12-18T01:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T06:41:13.000Z","uid":11512,"like":9,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9967dcf09bad7ae8fdc8b953be27fe0c08d7958a","tid":945442,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=i%2Eimgur%2Ecom%2FcdvY36y%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;errorredirect=i%2Eimgur%2Ecom%2FcdvY36y%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Di%252Eimgur%252Ecom%252FcdvY36y%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26errorredirect%3Di%252Eimgur%252Ecom%252FcdvY36y%252Ejpg&h=db6538b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙紅會氣氛熾烈，利物浦在狂攻之下卒之取得入球，以3-1 贏波。然而我覺得有需要教導一下大家：射波多，不等於應該贏波。方法是用Expected Goal。<br />\n大家都見我近期的文章整天講Expected Goal (xG)，計算每腳射門轉化為入球的機率，計算方程式頗為複雜。那為何要引用這個數據呢？原因是要引用數字說明射門質素。<br />\n<br />\n大家望到利物浦射門 36 次，總xG 2.61 就覺得利物浦抵贏。不過我先說明總xG 的盲點。<br />\n<br />\n盲點1：總xG 反映不到進攻質素<br />\n<br />\n大家要明白，xG 這個數據是 每腳射門xG的總和。如果你射100腳 xG 0.01(極低機率入)的射門，你的總xG 是 1；但是你射1腳 xG為 1(一定入)的射門，總xG 都是 1。相信你哋已經明個分別。<br />\n(我的定義：xG &lt;0.10 = 博大霧；xG 0.10 至 0.30 就叫正常機會；xG &gt;0.30 = 大好機會)<br />\n<br />\n利物浦今場的情況，當然是前者，但又能夠負負碌碌入到3球。36腳射門，只有4腳的 xG 大過 0.1 (入了1球，在禁區較大的藍星)，另外32腳就擺明博大霧的射門 (入了2球，其中兩個較少的藍星)。<br />\n<br />\n為何利物浦可以入到3球。這個時候可以運用中學不記得、大學都一定有的 sum, expected value &amp; variance 概念，解釋一下。<br />\n<br />\n100腳 0.01xG，即是這腳射門 (set) 包含兩個可發生結果 (possible outcome)，但只會中其中一項：99%入不到波，同埋1%入到波。數學寫法就是：{(0.99，0)，(0.01，1)}。然後將這個射門，即數學上的抽獎 (lottery，能否射入確實靠運) ，做100次。<br />\n<br />\n由於結果不是 0 就是 1，這情況即是 Bernoulli distribution。根據這分配方法，其平均值 (mean) 就是 p，即是成功 (即入波) 的機率，是 0.01；而變異數 (variance) 是 p 乘 q，是 0.0099。<br />\n<br />\n變異數的出現是因為：這個世界從來都不正常，可以說是從來都沒有正常這回事。引用《拾苟說足球》一句，&quot;if you don't buy the ticket, you don't win the raffle&quot;，即是說你腳風一順，100腳 xG 0.01 的射門全部都可射入龍門，入足100球。<br />\n<br />\n所以用平均數，我們就可以看得出利物浦製造出來的射門，其質素如何：2.61 &divide; 36 = 0.0725；曼聯就是 0.66 &divide; 6 = 0.11。曼聯射門平均質素居然比利物浦更好&hellip;&hellip;看來摩連奴可以藉此為自己平反一下&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n正因如此，所以總和比較可以反映的是比賽主導性，而非埋門、進攻質素。<br />\n<br />\n盲點2：總xG / 平均xG 會被獨立事項扯高<br />\n<br />\n那曼聯射門質素是否真的比利物浦好？無錯，這個正是xG的第2個盲點。<br />\n<br />\n一隊球隊總不會每腳都「40多碼，右腳腳面拉弓&hellip;&hellip; 」，然後就射100腳 xG 0.01 的射門。有得揀，當然是將射門位置推前，最好在門前射 &ndash; 因為入波機率一定較高。<br />\n<br />\n因此，一隊球隊每一場都會有不同 xG 的射門出現。有博大霧的射門、有正常攻門、還有大好機會。<br />\n<br />\n為何曼聯總xG 可達 0.66 呢？正因為 Lingard 把握 Alisson 甩手而補中的入球 (黃色大星)，和面對空門無異，就算眾人恥笑的前鋒如摩拉達都理應能夠入球 &ndash; 這球的 xG 有 0.53，佔曼聯總xG 的 80.3%。撇除這球，今場曼聯鋒線質素 (數據上) 確實與中下游球隊無異。<br />\n<br />\n正因為有獨立事項，變異數就可以話解釋到：這些數據有「鬼」喎。有「鬼」，梗要捉 - 所以為何曼聯的總xG 居然有 0.66，就此捉到隻「鬼」。<br />\n<br />\n相對之下，利物浦平均 xG 的變異數就細得多。反映利物浦近乎貼住每腳都有 7.25% 的或然率轉化為入波。雖然事實上有好多博大霧的遠射 (禁區外的藍色細圈)，大少少同好大的藍圈就只得幾個。<br />\n(變異數 Variance的計法/用途在此不贅，因其有分 Sample variance 及 Population variance，這些並非今日文章探討範圍之內)<br />\n<br />\n總xG 用途：反映賽果是否貼近現實<br />\n<br />\n每個射門是獨立的，每場賽事都是獨立的 &ndash; 將獨立事件加起來，方可見到整體，證明贏波是否實至名歸。<br />\n<br />\n每支球隊一季總會有好運的場次，亦會有不幸的場次。<br />\n<br />\n今場總結：<br />\n1. 利物浦全場圍攻，死攻爛攻，陷入拉鋸；因為有運，靠「博大霧」的射波方可致勝。<br />\n2. 證明遠射是破大巴一大有效方法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家多用 Expected Goals 作參考、多用腦，在各主流媒體向有關曼聯、皇馬、祖雲達斯等有不少 hater 的球隊之「新聞」整色整水時保持獨立思考。<br />\n<br />\n別讓腦袋生銹，別被媒體控制。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"382aae6e08c8762f6d7f1f6ac9cd05f010b9728c","tid":945442,"uid":121058,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"我獌又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905532cfea5e77af6eab2545d970e3aca88ef5bd","tid":945442,"uid":1823,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"咁睇曼聯真係雖敗猶榮"},{"pid":"aa8941597b921a53b8f1121b149149fdf1854df3","tid":945442,"uid":210728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dec841c95bf786dc80366f818bbc816af36e8a3","tid":945442,"uid":13391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n貴精不貴多<br />\n好似我曼咁6射入1球就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514fdfe2802638b9bb8d6fb540b3bae497cd4065","tid":945442,"uid":135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"唔係Alisson送大禮 最聯xG得0.13<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a323a08f7440b55c7d28fe5f2356d3281f4047f4","tid":945442,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔落reference? Link?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512436e4c8f9a17713b8a7eb89d1cbc5cc753718","tid":945442,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"希望曼迷們唔好再俾出面既post影響到<br />\n而家最緊要既係我地團結一致！！！"},{"pid":"e0c8353c764e3083c06bab44c2ce041fe2326220","tid":945442,"uid":53034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"512436e4c8f9a17713b8a7eb89d1cbc5cc753718","tid":945442,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:01:25.000Z","msg":"希望曼迷們唔好再俾出面既post影響到<br />\n而家最緊要既係我地團結一致！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"講得好！G持"},{"pid":"668ae482e1fc7ef4b411057ffe1a3d3de1481a8c","tid":945442,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"結論，曼聯或成為最終贏家"},{"pid":"e50b88ccffc385c6eaf8a076cea712be4c62fa0a","tid":945442,"uid":49222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"勁呀，成地精呀"},{"pid":"4a318200758972a994f388a9489d688c8da56f6f","tid":945442,"uid":177288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜鳩<br />\n輸波就係輸波啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3356771fa8f7ea19fbc2944f9e3b357ccbcf48af","tid":945442,"uid":32859,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:12:02.000Z","msg":"總結應該係 <br />\n利無運先贏得咁小<br />\n泊大巴無助球隊贏波"},{"pid":"7c2cd054e459b2c32df6b99004ffab197b65ef2d","tid":945442,"uid":168559,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"岩 識波既就知今場最聯其實贏左"},{"pid":"b346a1611aacdc7f7f05a9bced5b473c962330cd","tid":945442,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:15:59.000Z","msg":"勁！雖敗。猶榮！"},{"pid":"e4d460e3bd033a043e9e96109fcb753a2f455a74","tid":945442,"uid":203669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"爽啊！"},{"pid":"a80aab9dc1c358de900e1af650e20fb2101cf490","tid":945442,"uid":116643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"雖敗。猶榮"},{"pid":"e27702a3e54137ccf1d826b4bfbb46554a4eb5e8","tid":945442,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:04:32.000Z","msg":"勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1c1d7cb69a97b75ccf1325f668e0560149af8e","tid":945442,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAY4PpT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAY4PpT.png&h=03eda70f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14999f7201da21e52d0b13813acf742277b686de","tid":945442,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1c1d7cb69a97b75ccf1325f668e0560149af8e","tid":945442,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAY4PpT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAY4PpT.png&h=03eda70f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2a59002468015d227a87388916708412ebf26f","tid":945442,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XHmaK0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXHmaK0d.png&h=e0929d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19962b761cbbd311405fc9aebd18f74d83c64c08","tid":945442,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"算把啦<br />\n响連登貼學術post 咪又係得班抽水港豬回應"},{"pid":"961a7063510fef7e7487960d6f2780602b8bd58b","tid":945442,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"樓主一講conversion rate 壞話即刻食負評慘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6303ef79db4c11868bf7d79931f019100483774d","tid":945442,"uid":91325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"905532cfea5e77af6eab2545d970e3aca88ef5bd","tid":945442,"uid":1823,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:45:06.000Z","msg":"咁睇曼聯真係雖敗猶榮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:15:01.000Z","msg":"直頭應該判番曼聯贏"},{"pid":"da5bcba594356b5e3d1df57054026780145b823c","tid":945442,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"踢過波未啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}